trans-unit.source: Enables Compensating Resource Manger (CRM) on the tagged application.
trans-unit.target: 태그가 지정된 응용 프로그램에서 CRM(Compensating Resource Manger)을 사용합니다.

trans-unit.source: The following code example demonstrates the use of this attribute.
trans-unit.target: 다음 코드 예제에서는이 특성의 사용법을 보여줍니다.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.EnterpriseServices.CompensatingResourceManager.ApplicationCrmEnabledAttribute" /> class.

Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.EnterpriseServices.CompensatingResourceManager.ApplicationCrmEnabledAttribute" /> class, setting the <see cref="P:System.EnterpriseServices.CompensatingResourceManager.ApplicationCrmEnabledAttribute.Value" /> property to <see langword="true" />.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.EnterpriseServices.CompensatingResourceManager.ApplicationCrmEnabledAttribute" /> 속성을 <see langword="true" />로 설정하여 <see cref="P:System.EnterpriseServices.CompensatingResourceManager.ApplicationCrmEnabledAttribute.Value" /> 클래스의 새 인스턴스를 초기화합니다.

trans-unit.source: <see langword="true" /> to enable Compensating Resource Manager (CRM); otherwise, <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: CRM(Compensating Resource Manager)을 사용하려면 <see langword="true" />이고 그렇지 않으면 <see langword="false" />입니다.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.EnterpriseServices.CompensatingResourceManager.ApplicationCrmEnabledAttribute" /> class, optionally setting the <see cref="P:System.EnterpriseServices.CompensatingResourceManager.ApplicationCrmEnabledAttribute.Value" /> property to <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: 선택적으로 <see cref="T:System.EnterpriseServices.CompensatingResourceManager.ApplicationCrmEnabledAttribute" /> 속성을 <see langword="false" />로 설정하여 <see cref="P:System.EnterpriseServices.CompensatingResourceManager.ApplicationCrmEnabledAttribute.Value" /> 클래스의 새 인스턴스를 초기화합니다.

trans-unit.source: Enables or disables Compensating Resource Manager (CRM) on the tagged application.
trans-unit.target: 태그가 지정된 응용 프로그램에서 CRM(Compensating Resource Manager)을 사용할 수 있거나 사용할 수 없게 합니다.

trans-unit.source: <see langword="true" /> if CRM is enabled; otherwise, <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: CRM을 사용하면 <see langword="true" />이고, 그렇지 않으면 <see langword="false" />입니다.
